Instruct the heads of the implementing offices to act promptly on issues or constraints causing the non-implementation of the projects, prioritize and expedite the implementation of the subject projects to provide the expected benefits to the intended beneficiaries on time and maximize the use of the programs/projects;
Direct the Head of the Agency to make representation with DOLE for the approval to utilize the unexpended balances, if not, cause the return of the amount to the Bureau of Treasury; and
