Demand Mr. Ronel S. Baroy, Municipal Agriculturist and Ms. Pura A. Abadies, AT/Agribusiness Coordinator to render a satisfactory written explanation/justification on the deficiencies noted by the audit team especially on the involvement of DA Employee Multi-Purpose Cooperative on the mismanagement of the Municipal Food Terminal;

Require the incumbent Local Chief Executive to establish a system on the operation of the Municipal Food Terminal in coordination with the Office of the Municipal Agricultural Services (OMAS) and direct as follows:

The LCE to create an Operations and Maintenance Personnel to handle the MFT;

The LCE to designate an Operations Manager to monitor the compliance of the project;

The Head of the OMAS to encourage farmers and fisher folks to support and sustain the objectives of MFT; 

